      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Halfling&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Fearless, Halfling Luck&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>While most halflings are fearless, some are skittish, making them particularly alert. Halflings with this racial trait gain a +1 bonus on initiative checks and a +1 bonus on attack rolls when flanking. They take a ï¿½2 penalty on saves against fear effects and gain no benefit from morale bonuses on such saves. When affected by a fear effect, their base speed increases by 10 feet and they gain a +1 dodge bonus to Armor Class. This racial trait replaces fearless and halfling luck.</p>",
